<DocsPageTitle Path="Extensions/PasswordStrength">
    Blazorise PasswordStrength component
</DocsPageTitle>

<DocsPageLead>
    The <Code>PasswordStrength</Code> component combines a password input with configurable strength rules, a progress indicator, and localized guidance.
</DocsPageLead>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    The default setup follows passphrase-first guidance: long passwords are prioritized, common or breached values are blocked, and character-composition rules remain optional.
</DocsPageParagraph>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    To use the <Code>PasswordStrength</Code> component, install the <Code>Blazorise.Components</Code> package first.
</DocsPageParagraph>

